ses and `_controller.value == 0.0`, it returns `SizedBox.shrink()`. The `ServerU
rlTool` is disposed. When the drawer opens again, `ServerUrlTool` is recreated. 
`initState` reads the cubit state and initializes the controller.\n\nBUT, what i
f during the time the drawer is closed, something triggers `DevToolsWrapper` to 
