eUrl.isNotEmpty &&\n      _controller.text.isEmpty &&\n      !_focusNode.hasFocu
s,\n  listener: (context, state) {\n    _controller.text = state.serverBaseUrl;\
n  },\n```\n\nThis listener should NOT fire while the user is typing because:\n-
