BlocBuilder`? It rebuilds the widget, but the `TextEditingController` is separat
e from the widget build. Rebuilding doesn\'t change the controller text.\n\nWait
, what if `SwTextField` is recreating the `TextField` on every build, and someho
w the `TextField` is syncing its value from something other than the controller?
